      "span_text": "The conversion procedure converts the tokens to reflect the preferences that the subjects may have encountered each-other more than once over the course of the experiment, because the matching was anonymous, the possibility of colluding was minimized.  Since subjects were not aware of what was to happen in the next parts of the experiment, this procedure is identical to the original procedure of inducing risk-aversion with two prizes.",
